","score":1},{"id":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Bethel (of Palestine)","slug":"bethel_202","score":1},{"id":"reczeMGDnN4eb0Y28","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Ramah","slug":"ramah_975","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"rec4GS8yWh2R4mpdB","label":"part of"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recZsS2Zu0zIDwqdv","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"rec3McaFtR54oVD0n","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recjUsDi54y7u977Y","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recGdQVod5SbLO87Z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recVYcDguYN6bVqxy","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"rec8n4a7sEtrWBpaO","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recpk7ZvL6JuKqCqA","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recF5BKPMFrHnzfVq","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"rec3gWYVMktOUkAzZ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recDWNfN3f6E04V4m","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recdm9AlLF01lFAfP","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recSh1Wtk3yALG8di","target":"reczeMGDnN4eb0Y28","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recEghEfj56zFOtjo","ref":"1Sam.7.1","text":"And the men of Kirjathjearim came, and fetched up the ark of the LORD, and brought it into the house of Abinadab in the hill, and sanctified Eleazar his son to keep the ark of the LORD."},{"id":"recTRogSsk8A0YeqU","ref":"1Sam.7.2","text":"And it came to pass, while the ark abode in Kirjathjearim, that the time was long; for it was twenty years: and all the house of Israel lamented after the LORD."},{"id":"recHfER7FAgp7n9z5","ref":"1Sam.7.3","text":"And Samuel spake unto all the house of Israel, saying, If ye do return unto the LORD with all your hearts, then put away the strange gods and Ashtaroth from among you, and prepare your hearts unto the LORD, and serve him only: and he will deliver you out of the hand of the Philistines.","year":-1120},{"id":"recACeXIikCv0DO6N","ref":"1Sam.7.4","text":"Then the children of Israel did put away Baalim and Ashtaroth, and served the LORD only.","year":-1120},{"id":"recGhJbiiUU8Dwdt0","ref":"1Sam.7.5","text":"And Samuel said, Gather all Israel to Mizpeh, and I will pray for you unto the LORD.","year":-1120},{"id":"rechEmOP9Up7hlGv3","ref":"1Sam.7.6","text":"And they gathered together to Mizpeh, and drew water, and poured it out before the LORD, and fasted on that day, and said there, We have sinned against the LORD. And Samuel judged the children of Israel in Mizpeh.","year":-1120},{"id":"recCi0rpWluZCdFVj","ref":"1Sam.7.7","text":"And when the Philistines heard that the children of Israel were gathered together to Mizpeh, the lords of the Philistines went up against Israel. And when the children of Israel heard it, they were afraid of the Philistines.","year":-1120},{"id":"recJEcgbDBJEOpIiL","ref":"1Sam.7.8","text":"And the children of Israel said to Samuel, Cease not to cry unto the LORD our God for us, that he will save us out of the hand of the Philistines.","year":-1120}]}
